Clone this repo:

    git clone git@github.com:barneydesmond/dot-vim.git ~/.vim

Symlink vimrc into your homedir:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Now go install Vundle: https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim#quick-start

1. `git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim`
2. Add all your plugin calls to vimrc, this should already be in the repo.
3. Kick off the install: `vim +PluginInstall +qall`
